snippet.textDisplay: Let’s look back...10 years ago, backyard edition, 1st ever dude perfect video. They were probably like “ hey man we should totally make a YouTube channel called dude perfect!” Probably never thinking or wondering 10 years later, they have more than 40 million subscribers on YouTube, probably thinking they would only get a few hundred. Changing from a basketball hoop and a regular house on your normal neighborhood, to a massive Trick-shot making facility. All I’m saying is that you have no idea how things will change much in the course of maybe 10-20 years, I don’t know if these 5 amazing people would think that they would come to a position like this, and from going to a regular YouTube video, to a number 1 trending video. All in all, you have no idea how things can change, you may be having a rough patch in your life, but maybe a couple years later, you will be back to a nice, smooth patch. I just wanted to say to everyone, always believe in yourself because you have no idea how things can change.
